WertheimGCPM4PtThreeSiteEDecompDirectSampling.VirialAssociatingFluidParam

    public abstract class ParameterBase
extends java.lang.Object
    Base class for all parameter wrapper implementations. Subclasses should simply contain fields corresponding to each parameter. If any parameters are more complex than can be handled by this class, ParamParsers should be added to this object.
